{"tid":452281,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhoneX預訂數量破紀錄","createTime":"2017-10-30T04:38:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-30T06:53:19.000Z","uid":14953,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d582d32fcbfc084296dbef3f2e996825ab69d83e","tid":452281,"uid":14953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T04:38:54.000Z","msg":"上周五開始接受預訂的蘋果iPhone X，開放預訂後不久，便被搶購一空，價格更被炒高一倍。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果公司上周五宣布，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">iPhone X的預訂數量創紀錄新高</span></span>，但就無透露具體數字。<br />\n<br />\n不過市場擔心，由於面部解鎖技術生產難度大，產能未能達到預期標準，預計出貨時間可能會推遲。<br />\n<br />\nsouce：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/752150534977017/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F752150534977017%2F&d=smCtCamarhrpjCAdrbEdav1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=05f031f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/752150534977017/</a>"},{"pid":"dea588a8fafac91edf2c3333a16605f775dde0b3","tid":452281,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T04:44:48.000Z","msg":"係咁放假消息話無貨咪個個走去炒囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71550635c617cf054bb26c8be4d42c9788ab1cb1","tid":452281,"uid":141461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T05:47:45.000Z","msg":"apple 已死？"},{"pid":"5cf4158c46170553b66f937243d904b3b573bd9c","tid":452281,"uid":281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T05:48:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73288a2662fb992338c472211c257cdd57370942","tid":452281,"uid":124537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T05:55:20.000Z","msg":"增加出貨期就成功達成目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBTW, 香港係個别策略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99ebede1b94d92cbac0dc78ced1ada3837518f0c","tid":452281,"uid":11428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score